description: This data was creating using a program that checks what is trending at 2,000 latitute and longitude coordinates mine from Wikipedia. The coordinates are for sporting venues. A place only appears if 5 or more people have checked into a location. The category only picks up locations that have been put into a category related to the sport. It may not be accurate as a location may be mistagged or tagged with other categories. (Example: Eden Park in Auckland was tagged as a baseball stadium, not a football stadium. It appears under baseball. The United Center in Chicago appears under hockey and basketball.) Sporting events being played may not match the category.
